entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued October 03 at 1:42PM AKDT by NWS
entry.summary: ...Strong Storm Moving to the Eastern Bering Sea and Chukchi Sea Wednesday Through Friday... A strong storm will develop in the Sea of Ohkotsk tonight and move to Chukotsk Peninsula Wednesday, then to Wrangel Island by Thursday morning. The storm will continue northeast into the Arctic Ocean on Friday.
